37:51.917 --> 37:55.750
[Landry] She's pretty special,
isn't she?

37:55.750 --> 37:58.417
What?

37:58.417 --> 37:59.667
I said, she's pretty special,
isn't she?

37:59.667 --> 38:01.959
Natalie?

38:01.959 --> 38:05.583
Yeah.

38:05.583 --> 38:07.291
Hey, listen.

38:07.291 --> 38:11.375
Thanks for the other day.
I appreciate it.

38:11.375 --> 38:13.709
No problem.

38:13.709 --> 38:15.959
I'll see you later, Ray.

38:15.959 --> 38:20.125
♪♪♪

38:20.125 --> 38:24.667
[overlapping chatter]

38:24.667 --> 38:26.417
[director]
Okay, we're going again.

38:26.417 --> 38:28.125
Right away!

38:28.125 --> 38:29.667
[director] And action!

38:35.542 --> 38:38.291
[crickets chirping]

38:48.625 --> 38:51.375
What do you do, Ray?

38:51.375 --> 38:53.750
What do I do?

38:53.750 --> 38:55.750
Yeah, what do you do?

38:55.750 --> 38:56.250
[sighs]

38:56.250 --> 38:58.250
[soft chuckle]

38:58.250 --> 39:02.208
I work for people like you.

39:03.000 --> 39:04.208
People like me?

39:04.208 --> 39:07.166
What does that mean?

39:07.166 --> 39:11.333
What kind of things do you do
for people like me?

39:11.333 --> 39:15.208
When things go wrong,
I try to make 'em right.

39:15.208 --> 39:16.709
Yeah?

39:16.709 --> 39:18.375
Yeah.

39:18.375 --> 39:21.500
And what's the worst thing
I could ever do

39:21.500 --> 39:24.000
that would require the services

39:24.000 --> 39:26.208
of a certain Ray Donovan?

39:26.208 --> 39:28.166
Let me ask you something.

39:28.166 --> 39:30.375
Who were you running from
that night?

39:30.375 --> 39:33.417
My husband and I
got into a fight.

39:33.417 --> 39:36.000
Yeah?

39:36.000 --> 39:39.250
Where is he now?

39:39.250 --> 39:42.333
- We had another fight.
- [glass clinks]

39:46.375 --> 39:50.208
I got in this
really bad car accident

39:50.208 --> 39:52.875
a few years ago.

39:52.875 --> 39:57.041
I had this weird feeling that...

39:57.041 --> 39:59.417
...I had died,

39:59.417 --> 40:01.875
but they forgot to tell me.

40:01.875 --> 40:03.208
♪♪♪

40:03.208 --> 40:04.542
[soft scoff]

40:04.542 --> 40:05.959
And I was
wandering around like

40:05.959 --> 40:09.041
some ghost.

40:09.041 --> 40:14.208
♪♪♪

40:21.250 --> 40:23.834
What are you thinking, Ray?

40:26.625 --> 40:27.917
You seem really sad.

40:27.917 --> 40:30.625
Are you sad?

40:34.083 --> 40:36.000
Some days are just...
bad days.

40:36.000 --> 40:38.250
That's all.

40:38.250 --> 40:39.625
- I should go.
- [glass clinks]

40:41.959 --> 40:43.709
One more drink.

40:47.208 --> 40:50.917
We're just out
walking our dogs, right?

40:50.917 --> 40:53.542
Nothing more than that.

40:53.542 --> 40:57.667
♪♪♪

41:05.208 --> 41:07.959
[knock on door]

41:07.959 --> 41:10.125
Hey.

41:10.125 --> 41:13.250
Come on in.

41:14.250 --> 41:17.125
[door swings shut]

41:17.125 --> 41:18.291
