it was a good idea.

42:17.750 --> 42:20.375
Sure.

42:20.792 --> 42:22.667
[exhales]

42:22.667 --> 42:24.500
[softly]
I love you, baby.

42:24.500 --> 42:28.000
I'm gonna miss you, okay?
[kisses]

42:30.375 --> 42:31.792
Thanks.

42:36.041 --> 42:38.750
Ray.

42:47.667 --> 42:49.000
[door swings shut]

42:55.375 --> 43:01.375
- [coyote howls]
- [dogs bark]

43:03.875 --> 43:04.792
[soft groan]

43:09.667 --> 43:14.166
- [doorbell chimes]
- [clears throat]

43:15.583 --> 43:16.834
[sighs]

43:22.083 --> 43:25.000
She wants you to have him.

43:26.458 --> 43:29.291
